# Path → skill router

When editing a file matching one of these areas, read the matching domain skill
in `.agents/skills/` **before** writing. The root `AGENTS.md` is the master
router; this is a quick path-based reminder.

| Path / subsystem | Skill to read |
|---|---|
| `**/Audio/**`, `Resources/Audio/**`, sound playback | `.agents/skills/ss14-audio.md` |
| `**/Atmos/**`, gas/pipe/reaction/tile atmosphere | `.agents/skills/ss14-atmos.md` |
| `**/Movement/**`, `**/Physics/**`, transform, coords, collision | `.agents/skills/ss14-transform-physics.md` |
| PVs / entity visibility / "distant player can't see X" | `.agents/skills/ss14-pvs.md` |
| `**/BUI/**`, machine/console UIs | `.agents/skills/ss14-ui-bui.md` |
| `*.xaml`, client menus/windows | `.agents/skills/ss14-ui-xaml.md` |
| `**/EUI/**`, admin/player panels (non-entity) | `.agents/skills/ss14-ui-eui.md` |
| `**/Sprite/**`, `**/Overlays/**`, `*.swsl`, `GenericVisualizer` | `.agents/skills/ss14-sprite-overlays-shaders.md` |
| `Content.Server.Database/**`, migrations, persistence | `.agents/skills/ss14-databases-migrations.md` |
| `**/NPC/**`, HTN, pathfinding, mob behavior | `.agents/skills/ss14-npc-ai.md` |
| `Resources/Prototypes/**`, `Resources/Locale/**` | `.agents/skills/ss14-prototype-basics.md` |

Onboarding (read if unsure of basics): `ss14-ecs-basics.md`,
`ss14-client-server-shared.md`, `ss14-common-api-patterns.md`,
`ss14-debugging-workflow.md`, `ss14-porting-and-licensing.md`,
`ss14-ai-workflow.md`, `ss14-examples.md`.

Rules (mandatory, short) all live in `.agents/rules/`. Always read
`ss14-code-placement.md`, `ss14-fork-editing.md`, `ss14-ai-workflow.md`.
